title.rendered: Kenmaya – A  Full Winter Glacier Terrain

excerpt.rendered: Kenmaya is a small 2k Winter Glacier Survival Friendly Terrain for Java and Bedrock made by McMeddon. It contains galciers, pathways, iceflows and huge snowy forest alongside huge snow dunes.
